      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is offered in an exemplary state, reflecting a life of fastidious preservation and climate-controlled storage. From its flawless exterior finish to the showroom-fresh interior appointments, every detail adheres to the highest standards of mechanical and aesthetic excellence. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle that remains in its original, pristine configuration.",
      "price": 48500.0,
