    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It's in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the assembly line! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept spotless and pampered every single day. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s flawless and drives like a dream, this is the one. I\u2019m so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Come say hi and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
