      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a mechanically superlative E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox with precise, crisp linkage. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings to maintain optimal kinematic geometry, ensuring the factory limited-slip differential delivers power without chassis deflection. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing service and zero VANOS rattle, this vehicle represents a turn-key, investment-grade example for the performance-oriented purist.",
